#MEM id=rules source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/mia/skills/design-and-build/vercel-react-best-practices/rules/js-set-map-lookups.md
M|rules|title: Use Set/Map for O(1) Lookups
M|rules|impact: LOW-MEDIUM
M|rules|impactDescription: O(n) to O(1)
M|rules|tags: javascript, set, map, data-structures, performance
M|rules|Convert arrays to Set/Map for repeated membership checks.
M|rules|**Incorrect (O(n) per check):**
M|rules|```typescript
M|rules|const allowedIds = ['a', 'b', 'c', ...]
M|rules|items.filter(item => allowedIds.includes(item.id))
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Correct (O(1) per check):**
M|rules|```typescript
M|rules|const allowedIds = new Set(['a', 'b', 'c', ...])
M|rules|items.filter(item => allowedIds.has(item.id))
M|rules|```